        <mxCell id="9aEQQYlzqz-WVLYAH-7f-3" parent="1" style="whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="&lt;div style=&quot;language:en-GB;line-height:90%;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:6.0pt;&amp;lt;br/&amp;gt;margin-left:.31in;text-indent:-.25in;text-align:left;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:&amp;lt;br/&amp;gt;embed;mso-line-break-override:none;word-break:normal;punctuation-wrap:hanging&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 90%; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 6pt; text-indent: -0.25in; direction: ltr; word-break: normal;&quot;&gt;Make the layout in scale.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 90%; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 6pt; text-indent: -0.25in; direction: ltr; word-break: normal;&quot;&gt;(1) 11 loading stations, separated at 1m&amp;nbsp; each&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 90%; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 6pt; text-indent: -0.25in; direction: ltr; word-break: normal;&quot;&gt;(2) 11&amp;nbsp; unloading stations, separate at 1m each&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 90%; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 6pt; text-indent: -0.25in; direction: ltr; word-break: normal;&quot;&gt;(3) 20m between the loading station region and the unloading region&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 90%; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 6pt; text-indent: -0.25in; direction: ltr; word-break: normal;&quot;&gt;(4)&amp;nbsp; 3 Wireless Charging stations. One on the main loop, other two are in the charging loops.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 90%; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 6pt; text-indent: -0.25in; direction: ltr; word-break: normal;&quot;&gt;(5)&amp;nbsp;Total distance of a loop: 140 m or 130m or&amp;nbsp; 120m&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 90%; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 6pt; text-indent: -0.25in; direction: ltr; word-break: normal;&quot;&gt;(6) Please check the labeled distance in the layout picture (see the kickoff slide).&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
